name: FLORIDA RULES T-SHIRT
description:
You are pre-ordering a shirt dedicated to FLHC.  This first run will be limited to see how it goes over.  For this run the shirt will be navy with yellow ink.  Make sure you include your size when you order.  Leave it in the comments section.  Thanks!

I expect to have these within the next few weeks.

name: Cross Section 7" (1994)
description: Not what you would expect from a band from Syracuse, NY in the mid 90's.  4 tracks of heavy, yet melodic HARDcore.  Members went on to play in Earth Crisis.

name: Gunk 7" (1991)
description: you like Jawbreaker, and melodic punk bands?  Then this is for you!  4 songs that were released in 1991.  Members went on to play in Onion and other CT area bands.

name: Separate Peace/Junction split 7" (1991)
description:
found a few of these in my garage.  This is the 3rd release put out by Significant Records.  It was put out in 1991.  There were only 1000 of these pressed and I am selling 5 of these here instead of through Ebay.  Tracklist is as follows:
Separate Peace: Tool
Separate Peace: Jesse Helms' Green Hat
Junction: Saturation
Junction: Transit

If you are interested in a test pressing of this record, get in touch.

name: 5 cd's for $5.00!!!
description: I feel everyone should hear these releases so here is your chance to get alot of great music at a really cheap price.  You will get the following 5 cd's: Now Soldiers-"Sick World", Trample-"Strike When Provoked", Anchors Away-"Nuckin' Futs", Evasion-"Horizons" and the Haunted Life/Make Or Break-"Split".

name: Beneath The Wheel 7" (1990)
description:
found a handful of these in my garage.  This was the 1st 7" that was put out by Significant Records waaaay back in 1990.  This is a compilation, and has the following tracks:
Separate Peace: Take It All
Admiral-Comes From Nowhere
Greyhouse-Ashes
Zone One-Calling Dr. Love

These are extremely rare (as far as I know).  There are only 1000 of these out there and I am selling 3 here as opposed to Ebay.

name: In My Eyes: Live In Philly 7" (white-100 made/2002)
description:
found a few of these in my garage.  These are on white vinyl (100 made).  This was originally released in 2002.  Like the title says these are 6 live songs recorded in Philly.  Track list is:
Take The Risk
Actions Fall Short
Making Sense
Welcome To Boston
Through The Motions
My Reply

only handful available.  The picture shows the clear version, but these are on white.

name: box full of goodies.....(AKA garage sale)
description: I am cleaning out my garage.  I have tons of stuff in it.  So here is the deal, for $10.00 I will fill a box full of stuff from my garage including: cd's (at least 4),  stickers, posters (at least 2), Significant Records related shirt(s), could be Anchors Away, Take These Eyes, Make Or Break, Gator Bait, SigFest, Now Soldiers, DYDI or Trample (as long as I have your size), or a t-shirt from a random band, comics (at least 3) and other random good stuff....perhaps an action figure, some trading cards, vhs tape, a cool 7", demos, gift card, free show pass, other random stuff in my garage.  It has worked for other labels/bands, so I figured I'd give it a shot.  Make sure to specify your t-shirt size. Thanks.
